featured_reviews.review_id: A very active and beautiful ahle hadees mosque. The mosque regularly tries to host program on different topic, some which are specific for Women, some for Children and many general which are delivered by renowned scholars of ahlul hadeeth. There are basic aqeedah classes for children daily after Zuhr and Qur'an memorization for children and women daily after As'r salaah. This mosque has the hostel facility as well in third floor at a very reasonable rate including electricity and water. May Allaah aid the people and correct their mistakes and honour them who work towards facilitating such service to the Muslim Ummah.
